title: Learnex - Daily Video Vocabulary
description:
Learnex - Daily Video Vocabulary


WEBRip | English | MP4 | 1280 x 720 | AVC ~387 kbps | 25 fps
AAC | 126 Kbps | 44.1 KHz | 11:28:29 | 3.71 GB
Genre: eLearning Video / Linguistics, Study of Language

This series of video lessons will teach words. You learn the correct usage of sentence in context to the word and its meaning. Example sentences are presented at the end to explain you the correct usage of Grammar, which will make you a fluent English speaker.	
What is Learnex? Learnex is 'open' to students, language teachers and schools! Students can use Learnex to study on their tablet, smart phone, computer or smart TV. Learnex was founded in 2010 with the goal of using technology to help busy people learn new skills and English language
